(621, 1, '2018-09-04 06:22:09', '2018-09-04 06:22:09', '<p>\"The greatness of humanity is not in being human, but in being humane.”</p>		\n			<h2>-Mahatma Gandhi</h2>		\n			<h2>About us</h2>		\n		<p>For centuries, Orphanages and Old homes have been helpful in providing better lives for a great number of people around the world. Orphanages safeguard a healthy attachment or bond between children and the adults caring for them.Thus their chances of survival and a better quality of life are significantly improved.Elder care does an important service in the community in which the care is being provided, and can’t be overlooked for the essential service that it is. Our aim is to identify and categorize genuine orphanages that are striving hard to support the orphans, but lacking facilities and funds, making it difficult for them to provide better care to the children and also help them in finding loving families. Similarly we support old-age homes that are genuinely taking care of senior citizens, but in need of funds.People who want to adopt or help the institutions through donations can find all the required informations in this website which makes the whole process effortless.</p>		\n			<figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"66980377\" href=\'http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43820_800-1.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43820_800-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43820_800-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43820_800-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"66980377\" href=\'http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43001bw_800-1.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43001bw_800-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43001bw_800-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/IMG_A43001bw_800-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"66980377\" href=\'http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/6857040815_6405d4f535_b-1.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/6857040815_6405d4f535_b-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/6857040815_6405d4f535_b-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/6857040815_6405d4f535_b-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"66980377\" href=\'http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/81fd6c4ac886076555d06de6e1e5d60e-portrait-photography-tips-editorial-photography-1.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/81fd6c4ac886076555d06de6e1e5d60e-portrait-photography-tips-editorial-photography-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/81fd6c4ac886076555d06de6e1e5d60e-portrait-photography-tips-editorial-photography-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/81fd6c4ac886076555d06de6e1e5d60e-portrait-photography-tips-editorial-photography-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"66980377\" href=\'http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/8039272610_d8a0713181_c-1.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/8039272610_d8a0713181_c-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/8039272610_d8a0713181_c-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/8039272610_d8a0713181_c-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"66980377\" href=\'http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/imageggs-1.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/imageggs-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/imageggs-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/imageggs-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n			</figure>\n			<h2>HOW WE DO IT</h2>		\n										<img width=\"679\" height=\"1000\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/120af9bebdd0ee926bc8c9f6d8252405.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/120af9bebdd0ee926bc8c9f6d8252405.jpg 679w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/120af9bebdd0ee926bc8c9f6d8252405-204x300.jpg 204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Assemble\n				</h3>\n				<p>Collect necessary data about institutions in order to categorize.</p>\n				<h3>\n					AID\n				</h3>\n				<p>Cooperation with the   institutions to help them grow.</p>\n				<h3>\n					Deliver\n				</h3>\n				<p>Deliver to people who need it the most.</p>\n			<h3>MEET OUR TEAM</h3>		\n		<p>Every one of our team members is devoted to delivering the finest possible solutions.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/photo-1515462277126-2dd0c162007a-2-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/photo-1515462277126-2dd0c162007a-2-200x300.jpg 200w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/photo-1515462277126-2dd0c162007a-2-768x1150.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/photo-1515462277126-2dd0c162007a-2-684x1024.jpg 684w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/photo-1515462277126-2dd0c162007a-2.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" /></figure><h3>Mahbubur Rahman<br></h3><p>Developer</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/12993509_1062434300482946_4438259694667478420_n-1-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/12993509_1062434300482946_4438259694667478420_n-1-200x300.jpg 200w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/12993509_1062434300482946_4438259694667478420_n-1.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" /></figure><h3>Md Shamsujjaman</h3><p>Developer</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"240\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/38837030_480771859062856_5507308431901458432_n-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/38837030_480771859062856_5507308431901458432_n-240x300.jpg 240w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/38837030_480771859062856_5507308431901458432_n.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" /></figure><h3>Radiah Tahsin Tanisha</h3><p>Developer</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/14199232_1605338049766332_8166335682618581288_n-1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/14199232_1605338049766332_8166335682618581288_